code: public List<Header> getHeaders() {     List<Header> result = new ArrayList<>().     for (Map<String, String> inputHeader : headers) {         Map.Entry<String, String> entry = inputHeader.entrySet().iterator().next().         result.add(new Header(entry.getKey(), entry.getValue())).     }     return result. }
public void setWire(ByteString wire) {     this.wire = wire.hex(). }

@Override protected Case clone() throws CloneNotSupportedException {     Case result = new Case().     result.seqno = seqno.     result.wire = wire.     result.headers = new ArrayList<>().     for (Map<String, String> header : headers) {         result.headers.add(new LinkedHashMap<String, String>(header)).     }     return result. }
